! Warning: This list may break some functionality of AI tools. Use in a sandbox before definite use. 

! TOOL: SponsorBlock
! Main domains
@@||sponsor.ajay.app^$important
@@||api.sponsor.ajay.app^$important
@@||status.sponsor.ajay.app^$important
@@||web.sponsor.ajay.app^$important

